{"word":"G5611 - ὡραῖος - hōraîos - ho-rah'-yos - Beautiful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὡραῖος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hōraîos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ho-rah'-yos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Beautiful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அலங்கார, அழகான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"ripe, mature"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5610 - ὥρα - hṓra - ho'-rah/5610\">G5610</a>; <i>belonging</i> to the right <i>hour</i> or <i>season</i> (<i>timely</i>), that is, (by implication) <i>flourishing</i> (<i>beauteous</i> [figuratively]): - beautiful.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}